Word5 (1.4) stable; urgency=low

  * Polished some graphical effects.
  * Upgraded networking code for better leaderboard handling.
  * Slightly reduced VRAM usage.
  * Made graphics fill the screen, even if the window is not 4:3.
  * Made game detect optimal initial window size.
  * Changed license to GPL.
  * Updated documentation.
  * Added source code documentation.
  * Simplified loading screen.
  * Added copyright information to title screen.
  * Added keyboard menu navigation.
  * Renamed in-game 'chances' to 'lives' for clarity.
  * Changed fonts.
  * Changed logo and icon.
  * Added credits screen.

